00:16:29.990 --> 00:16:34.220
TAREK WILLIAM SAAB, Venezuelan Chief Prosecutor
(through translator): What happened last week,

00:16:34.220 --> 00:16:36.949
this electrical sabotage, is not a casual
event.

00:16:36.949 --> 00:16:41.939
What I am telling all of you is that it is
