00:17:57.600 --> 00:17:59.190
Mexico.

00:17:59.190 --> 00:18:02.090
President Trump is facing yet another investigation.

00:18:02.090 --> 00:18:06.960
It is widely reported that the New York state
attorney general's office has subpoenaed records

00:18:06.960 --> 00:18:08.390
from two banks.

00:18:08.390 --> 00:18:13.440
They involved real estate projects and Mr.
Trump's attempt to buy pro football's Buffalo

00:18:13.440 --> 00:18:15.960
Bills in 2014.

00:18:15.960 --> 00:18:20.930
His former lawyer Michael Cohen has told Congress
that the president routinely overstated his

00:18:20.930 --> 00:18:24.160
wealth when he was dealing with banks.

00:18:24.160 --> 00:18:26.490
And on Wall Street today, stocks had a mixed
